    "game-id": "99896cb8bb6b17c07e380946c2d0d3d0",
    "spell_type": "spell",
    "rank": 1,
    "text": "A violent wind issues forth from your palm, blowing from the point where you are when you Cast the Spell to the line's opposite end. The wind extinguishes small non-magical fires, disperses fog and mist, blows objects of light Bulk or less around, and pushes larger objects. Large or smaller creatures in the area must attempt a Fortitude save. Large or smaller creatures that later move into the gust must attempt the save on entering.",
